{
  "chapter": 82,
  "chapter_summary": "第八十二回「温柔陷阱」：白山君以假死之计骗过花无缺，花无缺被白夫人灌下宁神药后昏睡。三天后白夫人将花无缺送至一处幽谷，让他求见能救他性命的苏樱。花无缺进入幽谷后发现苏樱竟是一位年不满二十的少女，心中颇为失望，欲转身离去却被苏樱叫住。苏樱以冷静犀利的言语洞穿花无缺心思，指出他心脉将断、普天下仅三人能救。苏樱的房间布满机关，木童自动奉茶、铜灯自行点燃，令花无缺大为惊叹。二人就武功与智慧展开辩论，苏樱直言智慧高于武力。白夫人随后现身，透露众人的真实目的——骗出花无缺「移花接玉」的秘密。苏樱自信满满，认为以她独特的冷淡手段才能令花无缺就范，承诺次日便能让花无缺说出秘密。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "前辈端的是智计过人，弟子当真佩服得五体投地。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此计虽妙，也只有姓花的这种人才会上当，若换了你我，只怕再也不会如此轻易就相信女人的话。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "那人脾气甚是古怿，我……我不愿见他。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你可瞧见了那边的山亭？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "瞧见了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你转过这小亭，便可瞧见一面石门藏在山岩边的青藤里，石门终年不闭，你只管走进去无妨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "他叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "他叫苏樱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "苏樱……苏樱……我与你素不相识，却要求你来救我的性命，你只怕会觉得可笑。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你见着他后，他也许会问你是谁带来的，你只要说出我的名字……对了，我的本名是马亦云。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "我记得。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我此后虽生如死，你也不必再关心我，从今以后，世上再没有我这苦命的女人……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我此番纵然无故而死，但能死在这样的地方，也总算不虚此行了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能住在这种地方的，自然不会是俗人，我有幸能与高人相见，本是人生乐事，只可惜我现在竟如此模样。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我就是苏樱。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "山居幽僻，不知哪一位是阁下的引路人？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这……在下……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "阁下既然远道而来，难道连一句话都说不出么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "在下误入此间，打扰了姑娘的安静，抱歉得很……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "这位公子请留步。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘还有何见教？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你回来。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你并未误入此间，而是专程而来的，只不过见了苏樱竟是个少女后，你心里就有些失望了，是么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "就因为你是这种人，觉得若在个少女面前说出要求的事，不免有些丢人，所以你虽专程而来，却又借词要走，是么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你若是还要走，我自然也不能拦你，但我却要告诉你，你是万万走不出外面那石门的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "此刻你心脉已将被切断，面上已现死色，普天之下，已只有三个人能救得了你，而我……我就是其中之一，只怕也是惟一肯出手救你的，你若对自己的性命丝毫不知珍惜，岂非令人失望。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "现在已有床可以让你躺下了，你还要什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我……我想喝茶。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "呀，我竟忘了，有客自远方来，纵然无酒，但一杯茶的确是早该奉上的了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "抱歉得很，此间无茶，但这百载空灵石乳，勉强也可待客了，请。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "诸葛武侯的木牛流马，其巧妙只怕也不过如此了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "孔明先生的木牛流马，用于战阵之上倒是好的，若用于奉茶待客，就未免显得太霸气了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "难道姑娘不用动手，也能将灯燃起么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我是个很懒的人，懒得常会想出很多懒法子……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你瞧，我就算坐在这里不动，也可以做很多事的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "以我看来，纵然是自己燃灯倒茶，也要比造这些消息机关容易得多，你这懒人怎地却想出这最麻烦的法子？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "像我这样的人，难道也会替你倒茶么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你为何不用个丫环女仆，这法子岂非也容易得多？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我怕沾上那些人的俗气。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你说这些话，只因你觉得我太强了，所以想压倒我，是么？我不妨告诉你，世上没有人能压倒我的，我永远都是高高在上，你不必白费心机。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "其实你只不过是个弱不禁风的女孩子，任何人一掌就可以推倒你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你居然看我不会武功，你的眼光倒不错。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你的武功很不错，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "还过得去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但现在却是你要求我救你，我并没有求你救我。由此可见，世上有很多事，并不是武功可解决的。人所以为万物之灵，只因为他的智慧，并不是因为他的力气，若论力气，连匹驴子都要比人强得多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "现在，你老老实实地躺下去，我给你服下一瓶药后，你这可恶的笑声，立刻就可以停止了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "好妹子，真有你的，无论多么凶的男人，到了你面前都会乖得像只小狗……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你为何现在就来了，你不放心我？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "只不过大家都知道妹妹你心高气傲，所以要我来求妹妹，这次委屈些，只要这小子说出了'移花接玉'的秘密，咱们立刻就将这小子杀了给妹妹出气。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你觉得我对他这法子不好？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "不是不好，只不过……咱们现在是要骗他说出秘密，所以……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你觉得我应该对他温柔些，应该拍拍他马屁，灌灌他迷汤，必要时甚至不妨脱光衣服，倒入他怀里，是么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "反正这小子已快死了，就让他占些便宜又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "老实告诉你，我对他若真用这样的法子，他也是万万不肯说的，用这种法子来对付你的丈夫还差不多。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "但……但是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 82,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "对付他这样的人，就要用我这样的法子，他才服帖。只因我这样对付他，他就万万想不到我有事求他，也就万万不会提防我，否则我怎会故意让他看出我不会武功？你总该知道我虽不屑去学这些笨玩意儿，但要我装成一流高手的样子，我还是照样可以装得出的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 82,
